===Etymology===
From {{confix|xeno|phobe|lang=en}}. From {{etyl|grc|en}} {{term|ξένος||foreign, strange|lang=grc}}, + {{etyl|grc|en}} {{term|φόβος||fear|lang=grc}}.

===Pronunciation===
{{rfp|lang=en}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# One who [[fear]]s that which is [[unknown]]; one who fears [[people]] who are [[different]] from [[oneself]], [[especially]] in the case of [[foreign]] people.

